{"id":"eglaim","term":"Eglaim","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Two ponds, (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 15:8\">Isa. 15:8</a>), probably En-eglaim of <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 47:10\">Ezek. 47:10</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Isaiah 15:8","Ezekiel 47:10"]}